    " Recognition Pattern: This pattern provides the necessary data and information to create detailed schematics of the proposed design.",
    "Subsequently, the machine learning model can be trained on a large dataset of floor plans and corresponding features.",
    "This enables the model to generate new floor plans based on a set of input parameters.",
